                <position book_orientation="0" place="right_margin">
                    <marginalia_text> 
                        Eccè L[ucius] Sylla, vir terribilis, ingens, et sua tempestate mirabilis. Quantus belli, pacisq[ue] Pragmaticus?
                    </marginalia_text>
                <person name="Sulla"/>
                </position>
            </language>
            <translation>
                See Lucius Sulla, a formidable, very great man, extraordinary even in his own age. What a great pragmatic in war and peace! 
            </translation>
